abstract: "MumaxWriter.skill is a Codex/agent skill for writing, reviewing, parameterizing, and maintaining mumax3 .mx3 micromagnetic simulation scripts. It provides structured instructions, reusable templates, API pattern notes, anti-pattern checks, helper scripts, and evaluation examples for agent-assisted mumax3 workflows."
